can be distinguished from 
<taxonomicName authority="Rodríguez-Sánchez &amp; Giraldo-Kalil &amp; Quicke &amp; Zaldívar-Riverón, 2022" authorityName="Rodríguez-Sánchez &amp; Giraldo-Kalil &amp; Quicke &amp; Zaldívar-Riverón" authorityYear="2022" box="[898,1001,439,465]" class="Insecta" family="Braconidae" genus="Bracon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="72" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="laurae" status="sp. nov.">
