<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="73" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,151,321]" pageId="6" pageNumber="73">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,151,177]" pageId="6" pageNumber="73">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named after our dear colleague Rosamond Ione Coates Lutes, director of the the “Estación de Biología Tropical Los Tuxtlas” owned by the IBUNAM, for her great contribution to the study and conservation of the tropical rainforest in Los Tuxtlas, 
<collectingRegion box="[753,856,223,249]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="6" pageNumber="73">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[867,956,223,249]" name="Mexico" pageId="6" pageNumber="73">Mexico</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
